[{"location":"#OptimalBath","page":"Home","title":"OptimalBath","text":"Documentation for OptimalBath.\n\n","category":"section"},{"location":"#OptimalBath.BathymetryHandlingReconstruction","page":"Home","title":"OptimalBath.BathymetryHandlingReconstruction","text":"BathymetryHandlingReconstruction()\n\nA linear reconstruction similar to VolumeFluxes.LinearReconstruction, but caps heights and momentum to zero instead of adjusting the slope.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"type"},{"location":"#OptimalBath.DryFrontTerm","page":"Home","title":"OptimalBath.DryFrontTerm","text":"DryFrontTerm()\n\nA bottom topography source term corresponding to BathymetryHandlingReconstruction. Similar to the one used in VolumeFluxes, except that it balances the fluxes also at dry fronts, where the water height goes to zero.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"type"},{"location":"#OptimalBath.ForwardADGradient","page":"Home","title":"OptimalBath.ForwardADGradient","text":"ForwardADGradient(bathymetry::AbstractArray, β::AbstractArray)\n\nA gradient computation strategy using ForwardDiff for automatic differentiation. Stores two preallocated buffers: one for the bathymetry and one for the gradient results. The bathymetry starts as a copy of the initial bathymetry, and is updated during gradient computations.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"type"},{"location":"#OptimalBath.PrimalSWEProblem","page":"Home","title":"OptimalBath.PrimalSWEProblem","text":"PrimalSWEProblem(N, U0, T; initial_bathymetry=zeros(N + 1), domain=[0.0 1.0])\n\nA data structure representing the primal shallow water equations parameters.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"type"},{"location":"#OptimalBath.VolumeFluxesSolver","page":"Home","title":"OptimalBath.VolumeFluxesSolver","text":"VolumeFluxesSolver(spec::SolverSpec, float_type)\nVolumeFluxesSolver(problem::PrimalSWEProblem, options::SolverOptions, float_type)\nVolumeFluxesSolver(problem::PrimalSWEProblem, reconstruction, timestepper, bathymetry_source, float_type)\n\nA wrapper around VolumeFluxes's SWE solver.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"type"},{"location":"#OptimalBath.adjoint_solver","page":"Home","title":"OptimalBath.adjoint_solver","text":"adjoint_solver(primal_swe_problem::PrimalSWEProblem, ag::AdjointGradient) -> AdjointSolver\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"#OptimalBath.build_solver","page":"Home","title":"OptimalBath.build_solver","text":"build_solver(spec::SolverSpec[, float_type::Type=Float64])\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"#OptimalBath.compute_flux_source-NTuple{4, Any}","page":"Home","title":"OptimalBath.compute_flux_source","text":"compute_flux_source(Λ, Ul, Ur, Δx)\n\nComputes the source due to the reformulation of the adjoint pde to conservative form.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"#OptimalBath.compute_gradient!","page":"Home","title":"OptimalBath.compute_gradient!","text":"compute_gradient!(G, Λ, U, t, Δx, objectives::Objectives, ag::AdjointGradient)\ncompute_gradient!(G, Λ, Ul, Ur, t, Δx, objectives::Objectives, ag::AdjointGradient)\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"#OptimalBath.compute_objective","page":"Home","title":"OptimalBath.compute_objective","text":"compute_objective(U::States{S, Depth, T, N, A}, t, x, β, objectives::Objectives, timestepper::Timestepper) where {S, T, N, A}\ncompute_objective(U::States{S, Depth, T, N, A}, t, x, β, objectives::Objectives, timestepper::Type{<:Timestepper}) where {S, T, N, A}\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"#OptimalBath.compute_objective_and_gradient","page":"Home","title":"OptimalBath.compute_objective_and_gradient","text":"compute_objective_and_gradient(β, primal_swe_problem::PrimalSWEProblem, data::GradientData, ::GradientType)\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"#OptimalBath.compute_objective_and_gradient!","page":"Home","title":"OptimalBath.compute_objective_and_gradient!","text":"compute_objective_and_gradient!(G, β, primal_swe_problem::PrimalSWEProblem, data::GradientData, gradient_type::GradientType)\n\nAssigns the gradient of the objective function with respect to the parameters β into G, and returns the objective function value.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"#OptimalBath.compute_Δx","page":"Home","title":"OptimalBath.compute_Δx","text":"compute_Δx(solver::PrimalSWESolver)\n\nComputes the spatial discretization step size Δx for the given solver.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"#OptimalBath.create_callback","page":"Home","title":"OptimalBath.create_callback","text":"create_callback(f, solver::PrimalSWESolver)\n\nCreates a callback function for the given solver that applies the function f(U_n::States, t_n, Δt) at each time step during the primal solve.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"#OptimalBath.get_bathymetry","page":"Home","title":"OptimalBath.get_bathymetry","text":"get_bathymetry(solver::PrimalSWESolver)\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"#OptimalBath.get_gradient","page":"Home","title":"OptimalBath.get_gradient","text":"get_gradient(ad::ADGradient)\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"#OptimalBath.get_objective","page":"Home","title":"OptimalBath.get_objective","text":"get_objective(ad::ADGradient)\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"#OptimalBath.gradient!","page":"Home","title":"OptimalBath.gradient!","text":"gradient!(ad::ADGradient, f, β)\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"#OptimalBath.initial_state","page":"Home","title":"OptimalBath.initial_state","text":"initial_state(solver::PrimalSWESolver)\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"#OptimalBath.objective_density","page":"Home","title":"OptimalBath.objective_density","text":"objective_density(obj::Objective, U::States{S, Depth, T, N, A}, I...) where {S, T, N, A}\nobjective_density(::Objective, U)\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"#OptimalBath.objective_density_gradient","page":"Home","title":"OptimalBath.objective_density_gradient","text":"objective_density_gradient(obj::Objective, U::States{S, Depth, T, N, A}, I...) where {S, T, N, A}\nobjective_density_gradient(obj::Objective, U)\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"#OptimalBath.solve_adjoint","page":"Home","title":"OptimalBath.solve_adjoint","text":"solve_adjoint(Λ_end, U::AverageDepthStates, objectives::Objectives, b, t, Δx, da::AdjointSWE)\nsolve_adjoint(Λ0, Ul::LeftDepthStates, Ur::RightDepthStates, objectives::Objectives, b, t, Δx, da::AdjointSWE)\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"#OptimalBath.solve_primal","page":"Home","title":"OptimalBath.solve_primal","text":"solve_primal(solver::PrimalSWESolver, δb[, callback])\n\nSolves the primal shallow water equations with the provided solver given the change δb in bathymetry, returning the solution U, time points t, and spatial points x.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"#OptimalBath.update_and_get_bathymetry!","page":"Home","title":"OptimalBath.update_and_get_bathymetry!","text":"update_and_get_bathymetry!(ad::ADGradient, swe_problem::PrimalSWEProblem, indices, β)\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"}]
